### Submit async vectorization task
POST http://localhost:8080/api/rag/documents/1/vectorize-async


### Get embedding task by taskId
GET http://localhost:8080/api/rag/embedding-tasks/1


### List embedding tasks of document
GET http://localhost:8080/api/rag/documents/1/embedding-tasks


### Ask after async vectorization
POST http://localhost:8080/api/rag/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "spaceId": 1,
  "question": "What is the service layer used for?",
  "topK": 5
}